       <h1>
        Welcome to Metallurgical Engineering!
       </h1>
       <hr/>
       <p>
        Metallurgical Engineers transform metals into products useful for society. Metallurgists
                        are constantly thinking of new ways to minimize waste, maximize energy efficiency,
                        increase performance and facilitate recycling.
        <a href="/about/index.php">
         Learn more!
        </a>
       </p>
       <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="/about/index.php">
         <img alt="What is Metallurgical Engineering: Mineral Processing, Extractive Metallurgy, Physical Metallurgy" src="/_images/met_eng/whatismet.jpg" width="100%"/>
        </a>
       </p>
